pageInfo.title: Using a Gameboy for AI Development
pageInfo.body: I needed to do a semester project for my AI class but I also wanted to do something with the Gameboy emulator that I was working on at the time so I had the bright idea to create an AI that can play the Gameboy. My group partner Michael Knight and I wanted to go all out and create the hardest AI that we were able to find. This is what we turned in at the end:
